description: Our Mission is to make Indian food simple, fast and healthy.We are passionate about sharing with you, the home cooked, deliciousand healthy Indian food we grew up eating.Bombay Wraps has taken the best of Indian food - complex flavors, abundantvariety and delicious slow cooked recipies and made it simple, fast andhealthy by wrapping our favorite Indian dishes in a flatbread (flaky layeredparatha or 100% whole wheat roti).Join us for some Fresh, Indian Food, Fast.We have simplified Indian food by wrapping popular dishes like Chicken Tikka, Cheese Paneer, Lamb Curry, etc. in a flatbread paratha.
name: Bombay Wraps
